{"tid":190132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不斷更新】習特會正式展開 晚上共晉燭光晚餐","createTime":"2017-04-07T02:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T06:21:03.000Z","uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48640cd865005e3da03d1f0839cedbc02d75a4a5","tid":190132,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491525099_40b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491525099_40b6.jpg&h=69cf4dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普夫妻的紅色組合，與習近平夫妻的藍色組合。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491523461_ba1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491523461_ba1b.jpg&h=e0db5c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普今日打上大紅色的領帶，會見打藍色領帶的習近平。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491523462_11b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491523462_11b1.jpg&h=952f8466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普與習近平熱情握手。 <br />\n<br />\n「習特會」今日展開，國家主席習近平抵達美國佛羅里達州棕櫚灘，與美國總統特朗普進行24小時旋風式會晤。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n07:23：路透社報道，特朗普在晚宴上發表演說，他相信與國家主席習近平將會有一個「非常、非常好的長遠友誼」，在明日的私人會面時，開玩笑指：「至今我沒有得到甚麼，一無所有」。 <br />\n<br />\n07:00：特朗普打上大紅色的領帶，夫人梅拉尼婭則是一襲吊帶紅裙，迎接習近平夫婦。而習近平則是打上藍色領帶，夫人彭麗媛則是一襲深藍色旗袍，與梅拉尼婭相比，比較密實。（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2oP7PKz）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oP7PKz%EF%BC%89&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ca2f9596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2oP7PKz）</a> <br />\n06:30：習近平和特朗普攜眷共晉燭光晚餐。（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2oeXEB4）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oeXEB4%EF%BC%89&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=294aab20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2oeXEB4）</a> <br />\n<br />\n06:00：中國訪民到莊園和習近平下榻酒店拉橫額抗議，中國使館派員監視，有訪民遭美國警方帶走，但傍晚已獲釋。（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nQe2oR）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nQe2oR%EF%BC%89&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2276404b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nQe2oR）</a> <br />\n<br />\n05:00：習近平伉儷前往特朗普的私人度假村馬阿拉歌莊園（Mar-a-Lago）內，與特朗普及其夫人梅拉尼婭會面。習近平下車時，特朗普親自迎接，雙方握手，四人之後大門前合照，特朗普不時展露笑容。四人稍後進行較輕鬆會面並相互了解，特朗普夫人梅拉尼婭會邀彭麗媛茶敍。 <br />\n<br />\n01:50：習近平夫婦乘坐的專機抵達佛羅里達州西棕櫚灘國際機場，受到美國國務卿蒂勒森夫婦等接機。習近平與身穿黑色外套的彭麗媛在簡短軍禮歡迎儀式後，驅車前往下榻酒店「水棕櫚海灘度假村」（Eau Palm Beach Resort and Spa）。"},{"pid":"211cbd881282be2cc68716ddea069fc548e5ad3a","tid":190132,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:20:56.000Z","msg":"露肩清涼風vs密實中國風 兩位夫人大不同 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491523954_700a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491523954_700a.jpg&h=bb503727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梅拉尼婭身穿紅色露肩連身裙，彭麗媛則穿上深藍色旗袍。(互聯網) <br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普本港時間凌晨於佛州的私人度假村，會晤中國國家主席習近平。（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nQkCvd）雙方的夫人也隨行在側，這是特朗普首次和習近平的會面，也是媒體聚焦的焦點。當然，兩位夫人的服裝搭配，更是鏡頭不能錯過的重點。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nQkCvd%EF%BC%89%E9%9B%99%E6%96%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%AB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E9%9A%A8%E8%A1%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%81%B4%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%92%8C%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%83%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E8%81%9A%E7%84%A6%E7%9A%84%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E3%80%82%E7%95%B6%E7%84%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%A9%E4%BD%8D%E5%A4%AB%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%8D%E8%A3%9D%E6%90%AD%E9%85%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%9B%B4%E6%98%AF%E9%8F%A1%E9%A0%AD%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E9%8C%AF%E9%81%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E9%BB%9E%E3%80%82&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3115ec14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nQkCvd）雙方的夫人也隨行在側，這是特朗普首次和習近平的會面，也是媒體聚焦的焦點。當然，兩位夫人的服裝搭配，更是鏡頭不能錯過的重點。</a> <br />\n<br />\n特朗普夫人梅拉尼婭和習近平夫人彭麗媛，兩人有一個共通點，都曾是舞台上的明星。梅拉尼婭是前名模，彭麗媛也曾是表演藝術家，兩人今日的登場與服裝的穿着，都免不了被媒體比一比，可謂夫人版的「名模生死鬥」。 <br />\n<br />\n梅拉尼婭與特普從馬里蘭州抵達佛州時，以一襲黑底白碎花的深V露肩連身裙，配黑色粗皮帶，展現在媒體鏡頭前。當她接見習近平夫婦時，則是換上大紅色露肩小洋裝。相較於梅拉尼婭的清涼風格，彭麗媛的服裝就相對保守。 <br />\n<br />\n她和習近平下機時，以白色套裝搭配白鞋、白色手袋，外搭一件黑色外套，加上深藍色圍巾露面，而與特朗普夫婦見面時，她則換上「中國風」的深藍色旗袍。兩位夫人的穿着，各有風味。 <br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491523955_513a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491523955_513a.jpg&h=e8e50098&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n梅拉尼婭稍早下機時，身穿黑白配深V露肩連身裙。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491523956_fdd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491523956_fdd7.jpg&h=6e344c81&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n彭麗媛抵美時也是黑白配，但穿着相對保守。"},{"pid":"1f712361f67879694f78f9f577c87c2519ca5b11","tid":190132,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:21:31.000Z","msg":"【習特會】「女神」伊萬卡畀面同行 帶埋3囝囡現身 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526144_a488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526144_a488.jpg&h=fbde3a28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526147_a9ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526147_a9ba.jpg&h=1efffe53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526149_007a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526149_007a.jpg&h=99f9dff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普首度與中國國家主席習近平會面，舉世矚目。（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nQkCvd）而引人關注的，還有特朗普長女伊萬卡，帶着3名子女隨機抵達棕櫚灘。此前在日本首相安倍晉三訪美時，伊萬卡也沒有帶着小孩現身。而特朗普夫婦在莊園設晚宴款待習近平及夫人彭麗媛，預計身為總統助理的伊萬卡也會出席。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nQkCvd%EF%BC%89%E8%80%8C%E5%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E9%95%B7%E5%A5%B3%E4%BC%8A%E8%90%AC%E5%8D%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%B6%E7%9D%803%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E9%9A%A8%E6%A9%9F%E6%8A%B5%E9%81%94%E6%A3%95%E6%AB%9A%E7%81%98%E3%80%82%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D%E5%9C%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E5%AE%89%E5%80%8D%E6%99%89%E4%B8%89%E8%A8%AA%E7%BE%8E%E6%99%82%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%8A%E8%90%AC%E5%8D%A1%E4%B9%9F%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%B6%E7%9D%80%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A9%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%E3%80%82%E8%80%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E5%9C%A8%E8%8E%8A%E5%9C%92%E8%A8%AD%E6%99%9A%E5%AE%B4%E6%AC%BE%E5%BE%85%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%8A%E5%A4%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%BD%AD%E9%BA%97%E5%AA%9B%EF%BC%8C%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E8%BA%AB%E7%82%BA%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%8A%E8%90%AC%E5%8D%A1%E4%B9%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E3%80%82&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=17f20b5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nQkCvd）而引人關注的，還有特朗普長女伊萬卡，帶着3名子女隨機抵達棕櫚灘。此前在日本首相安倍晉三訪美時，伊萬卡也沒有帶着小孩現身。而特朗普夫婦在莊園設晚宴款待習近平及夫人彭麗媛，預計身為總統助理的伊萬卡也會出席。</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526146_977a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526146_977a.jpg&h=27182f3d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》中文網報道稱，在美國，伊萬卡已經成為一個頗具爭議的人物，要應對接連不斷的有關商業衝突的質疑，被批評沒有做更多努力以緩和她父親針對女性的政策。但在中國，伊萬卡卻受到普遍的喜愛。她奢華的生活方式和出色的商業頭腦，引發了許多渴望獲得聲名與財富的年輕職業人士的共鳴。 <br />\n不僅如此，伊萬卡還在社交媒體上被封為「女神」。一段她女兒唱中文歌的影片在網上瘋傳開來，吸引了數千萬人觀看，有網民留言評價：「未當選時就很欣賞她。人格魅力。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526145_4d4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526145_4d4f.jpg&h=302d0663&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n職場媽媽們熱情地接受伊萬卡那擁有一切的女性主義品牌，儘管她們大多缺乏跟她一樣的財力；企業家們則研究她的演講，想從中找到實現成功宣傳的秘訣。在科技和金融等行業工作的年輕中國女性尤其喜愛伊萬卡，她們將其看作兼具實力與雄心的優雅象徵。她們表示，在面對職場和家庭生活中的沙文主義與模式化觀念時，她們會努力效仿她的堅韌與自信。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526150_eb30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526150_eb30.jpg&h=f30bb12d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報道稱，許多人也十分欽佩伊萬卡決定開創自己的時尚品牌，而非僅僅專注於家族地產生意。 <br />\n鳳凰衛視"},{"pid":"388ebaa524e7572504bd50c4c4365b3e907faf6a","tid":190132,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:23:29.000Z","msg":"【習特會】近百名示威者抗議 促關注中國人權 <br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平抵達美國佛州，與美國總統特朗普舉行首次峯會。（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nQkCvd）約100人趁習近平到訪，到佛羅里達州習近平下榻的酒店「水棕櫚海灘度假村」（Eau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nQkCvd%EF%BC%89%E7%B4%84100%E4%BA%BA%E8%B6%81%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%88%B0%E8%A8%AA%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%B0%E4%BD%9B%E7%BE%85%E9%87%8C%E9%81%94%E5%B7%9E%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%8B%E6%A6%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E3%80%8C%E6%B0%B4%E6%A3%95%E6%AB%9A%E6%B5%B7%E7%81%98%E5%BA%A6%E5%81%87%E6%9D%91%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%88Eau&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=5e682020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nQkCvd）約100人趁習近平到訪，到佛羅里達州習近平下榻的酒店「水棕櫚海灘度假村」（Eau</a> Palm Beach Resort and Spa） 外抗議，敦促特朗普向習近平表達關注中國的人權狀況，以及停止逼害維權人士。 <br />\n<br />\n海外媒體博訊新聞網報道，在美國時間下午2時許（香港時間清晨2時許），中國訪民馬永田在莊園外，疑遭中國大使館派人跟蹤。來自上海的企業家、訪民袁建斌，則被美國警察帶離現場，中方人員指袁「偷走」國旗，事實是他看到美國國旗在地上撿起。另外，李煥君、賈闊也被警方帶走調查，但至當地時間傍晚6時許已一起獲釋。 <br />\n<br />\n博訊聞新聞網 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526514_d8cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526514_d8cd.jpg&h=6ce444c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526484_1a5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526484_1a5b.jpg&h=f0868dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526485_b10b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526485_b10b.jpg&h=3fcf2c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526486_7ffd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526486_7ffd.jpg&h=17039dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526486_c622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526486_c622.jpg&h=da875f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526487_5f13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526487_5f13.jpg&h=db292b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526488_36b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526488_36b5.jpg&h=2048c694&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39c3ee63f04805e5f64db6e78bb95b8ab08779be","tid":190132,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:23:50.000Z","msg":"佛州莊園首會共晉晚餐 特朗普：已跟習近平建立友誼 <br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平結束芬蘭國是訪問後，本港時間凌晨飛抵美國佛羅里達州棕櫚灘與美國總統特朗普作24小時旋風式會晤，在特朗普的私人莊園首度會面。 <br />\n<br />\n習近平與隨員乘坐的專機，香港時間約凌晨1時30分降落棕櫚灘國際機場，習近平和夫人彭麗媛受到美國國務卿蒂勒森夫婦等迎接，禮兵分列紅地毯兩側。習近平與身著黑色外套的彭麗媛在簡短軍禮歡迎儀式後，驅車前往下榻飯店「水棕櫚海灘度假村」（Eau Palm Beach Resort and Spa）。特朗普較早時冒雨登上空軍一號專機，由馬里蘭州前往佛州與習近平會晤。 <br />\n<br />\n習近平夫婦於當地下午約5時（香港時間清晨5時），前往特朗普的私人度假村馬阿拉歌莊園（Mar-a-Lago）內，與特朗普及其夫人梅拉尼婭會面。習近平下車時，特朗普親自迎接，雙方握手，四人之後在大門前合照，特朗普不時展露笑容。 <br />\n<br />\n四人稍後進行較輕鬆會面並相互了解，第一夫人梅拉尼婭會邀彭麗媛茶敍，晚上6時半（香港時間早上6時半）習特各偕夫人共晉晚餐。晚宴上特朗普坐習近平左邊，戲稱與習近平初見面後一無所獲，卻與對方建立起友誼，期望雙方能發展長期的良好關係。 <br />\n<br />\n翌日習特兩人會在莊園內舉行一系列工作會議，習並在與特朗普共晉午餐後啟程回國，訪問會歷時約24小時。 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普將就北韓問題和中美貿易不平衡向習施壓，外界預料會面為未來半世紀的中美關係發展確立方向。特朗普前往佛州前向霍士新聞表示：「這次會面將會很有趣。無人知會發生甚麼事。」他又再度對雙方的貿易關係表示不滿。 <br />\n<br />\n白宮亞洲事務專家波廷杰（Matt Pottinger）表示，中美雖然因貿易和北韓問題而關係緊張，但保證習特將在輕鬆氣氛下交流。 <br />\n<br />\n法新社／路透社／美聯社"},{"pid":"57756211fd82bc0b262d191e489684847a05b4a9","tid":190132,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491525672_4a19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491525672_4a19.jpg&h=a34ef169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491517992_e261.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491517992_e261.jpg&h=b4f05040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491501451_489f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491501451_489f.jpg&h=25beda2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平專機抵達佛州棕櫚灘國際機場 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491501185_9680.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491501185_9680.jpg&h=3015eddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普中午冒雨登上空軍一號專機，由馬里蘭州前往佛州與習近平會晤。"},{"pid":"c48b086db61bb81174fb478f97b33f9d429162f8","tid":190132,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:24:37.000Z","msg":"晚宴食啲乜？ 主菜有紐約客牛扒 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491528644_cf07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491528644_cf07.jpg&h=c7289c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491528646_c9da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491528646_c9da.jpg&h=539c1e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在馬阿拉歌莊園（Mar-a-Lago）內宴請國家主席習近平伉儷，究竟白宮預備了甚麼菜式？以下是晚宴餐單： <br />\n<br />\n凱撒沙律 <br />\n香檳煎比目魚 <br />\n香草焗薯 <br />\n青豆紅蘿蔔 <br />\n（或） <br />\n紐約客牛扒 <br />\n薯茸 <br />\n焗根類蔬菜 <br />\n甜品選擇： <br />\n朱古力蛋糕伴雲尼拿醬和黑朱古力雪芭 <br />\n（或） <br />\n雪芭三重奏（檸檬、芒果、紅莓） <br />\n酒類選擇： <br />\n白酒（2014 Chalk Hill Chardonnay from the Sonoma Coast） <br />\n紅酒 （Girard Cabernet Sauvignon, Napa Valley）"},{"pid":"b6f7533648ce13dcb66dac0339e322d48d81bcc0","tid":190132,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:26:46.000Z","msg":"岩岩對syria射左70支missile<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓艦艇駛入南海島礁<br />\n<br />\n呢場大戲好睇"},{"pid":"422041957e25448a15d105cf321772d859788574","tid":190132,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩對syria射左70支missile<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓艦艇駛入南海島礁<br />\n<br />\n呢場大戲好睇</blockquote><br />\n2017 - 2003 = 14 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9419f340869f4256a1d38a999ac09491877970","tid":190132,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩對syria射左70支missile<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓艦艇駛入南海島礁<br />\n<br />\n呢場大戲好睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIS?對syria射missile?<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓海軍陸戰隊是否已經佔領多個無人島嶼?"},{"pid":"b4ba3d86a5f868ae4d007655e61acfbe683e3d07","tid":190132,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩對syria射左70支missile<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓艦艇駛入南海島礁<br />\n<br />\n呢場大戲好睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<del>IS?</del> 美國對syria射missile?<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓海軍陸戰隊是否已經佔領多個無人島嶼?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c9bc75d73d53ef95e98c76e000e048209ca4b74b","tid":190132,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:37:35.000Z","msg":"侵侵之前唔係話只請雜總食老麥架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b033422ef7a5b9fbfbdc72613d5774900af6a96","tid":190132,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:38:18.000Z","msg":"食完仲有煙花睇，唔知習大大對餐飯滿唔滿意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c736db47b3ff5251f7a184d4ac92ec241d3954","tid":190132,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>晚宴食啲乜？ 主菜有紐約客牛扒 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491528644_cf07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491528644_cf07.jpg&h=c7289c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491528646_c9da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491528646_c9da.jpg&h=539c1e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在馬阿拉歌莊園（Mar-a-Lago）內宴請國家主席習近平伉儷，究竟白宮預備了甚麼菜式？以下是晚宴餐單： <br />\n<br />\n凱撒沙律 <br />\n香檳煎比目魚 <br />\n香草焗薯 <br />\n青豆紅蘿蔔 <br />\n（或） <br />\n紐約客牛扒 <br />\n薯茸 <br />\n焗根類蔬菜 <br />\n甜品選擇： <br />\n朱古力蛋糕伴雲尼拿醬和黑朱古力雪芭 <br />\n（或） <br />\n雪芭三重奏（檸檬、芒果、紅莓） <br />\n酒類選擇： <br />\n白酒（2014 Chalk Hill Chardonnay from the Sonoma Coast） <br />\n紅酒 （Girard Cabernet Sauvignon, Napa Valley）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCHEAP到呀.."},{"pid":"19e970aa7a5ece81c175c09468289bed46f92c50","tid":190132,"uid":101461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>晚宴食啲乜？ 主菜有紐約客牛扒 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491528644_cf07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491528644_cf07.jpg&h=c7289c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491528646_c9da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491528646_c9da.jpg&h=539c1e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在馬阿拉歌莊園（Mar-a-Lago）內宴請國家主席習近平伉儷，究竟白宮預備了甚麼菜式？以下是晚宴餐單： <br />\n<br />\n凱撒沙律 <br />\n香檳煎比目魚 <br />\n香草焗薯 <br />\n青豆紅蘿蔔 <br />\n（或） <br />\n紐約客牛扒 <br />\n薯茸 <br />\n焗根類蔬菜 <br />\n甜品選擇： <br />\n朱古力蛋糕伴雲尼拿醬和黑朱古力雪芭 <br />\n（或） <br />\n雪芭三重奏（檸檬、芒果、紅莓） <br />\n酒類選擇： <br />\n白酒（2014 Chalk Hill Chardonnay from the Sonoma Coast） <br />\n紅酒 （Girard Cabernet Sauvignon, Napa Valley）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCHEAP到呀..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n青豆紅蘿蔔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  笑咗"},{"pid":"00b41b9b208016a6ce8b9a9773bf572faf621bbc","tid":190132,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【習特會】「女神」伊萬卡畀面同行 帶埋3囝囡現身 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526144_a488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526144_a488.jpg&h=fbde3a28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526147_a9ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526147_a9ba.jpg&h=1efffe53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526149_007a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526149_007a.jpg&h=99f9dff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普首度與中國國家主席習近平會面，舉世矚目。（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nQkCvd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nQkCvd&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a26de910\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nQkCvd</a>）而引人關注的，還有特朗普長女伊萬卡，帶着3名子女隨機抵達棕櫚灘。此前在日本首相安倍晉三訪美時，伊萬卡也沒有帶着小孩現身。而特朗普夫婦在莊園設晚宴款待習近平及夫人彭麗媛，預計身為總統助理的伊萬卡也會出席。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526146_977a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526146_977a.jpg&h=27182f3d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》中文網報道稱，在美國，伊萬卡已經成為一個頗具爭議的人物，要應對接連不斷的有關商業衝突的質疑，被批評沒有做更多努力以緩和她父親針對女性的政策。但在中國，伊萬卡卻受到普遍的喜愛。她奢華的生活方式和出色的商業頭腦，引發了許多渴望獲得聲名與財富的年輕職業人士的共鳴。 <br />\n不僅如此，伊萬卡還在社交媒體上被封為「女神」。一段她女兒唱中文歌的影片在網上瘋傳開來，吸引了數千萬人觀看，有網民留言評價：「未當選時就很欣賞她。人格魅力。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526145_4d4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526145_4d4f.jpg&h=302d0663&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n職場媽媽們熱情地接受伊萬卡那擁有一切的女性主義品牌，儘管她們大多缺乏跟她一樣的財力；企業家們則研究她的演講，想從中找到實現成功宣傳的秘訣。在科技和金融等行業工作的年輕中國女性尤其喜愛伊萬卡，她們將其看作兼具實力與雄心的優雅象徵。她們表示，在面對職場和家庭生活中的沙文主義與模式化觀念時，她們會努力效仿她的堅韌與自信。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491526150_eb30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491526150_eb30.jpg&h=f30bb12d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報道稱，許多人也十分欽佩伊萬卡決定開創自己的時尚品牌，而非僅僅專注於家族地產生意。 <br />\n鳳凰衛視</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7ba7387f39c5cb4941ddc95fdb025626deb454","tid":190132,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>晚宴食啲乜？ 主菜有紐約客牛扒 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491528644_cf07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491528644_cf07.jpg&h=c7289c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491528646_c9da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491528646_c9da.jpg&h=539c1e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在馬阿拉歌莊園（Mar-a-Lago）內宴請國家主席習近平伉儷，究竟白宮預備了甚麼菜式？以下是晚宴餐單： <br />\n<br />\n凱撒沙律 <br />\n香檳煎比目魚 <br />\n香草焗薯 <br />\n青豆紅蘿蔔 <br />\n（或） <br />\n紐約客牛扒 <br />\n薯茸 <br />\n焗根類蔬菜 <br />\n甜品選擇： <br />\n朱古力蛋糕伴雲尼拿醬和黑朱古力雪芭 <br />\n（或） <br />\n雪芭三重奏（檸檬、芒果、紅莓） <br />\n酒類選擇： <br />\n白酒（2014 Chalk Hill Chardonnay from the Sonoma Coast） <br />\n紅酒 （Girard Cabernet Sauvignon, Napa Valley）</blockquote><br />\